         JNE   SCHINIX                                                          
         J     SCHINI04                                                         
                                                                                
SCHINI03 L     R4,AIO2                                                          
         MVC   CSVKEY1,0(R4)                                                    
         MVC   IOKEY,0(R4)                                                      
         LA    R4,IOKEY                                                         
         GOTOR (#IOEXEC,AIOEXEC),'IOHI+IODIR+IO2'                               
         JNE   *+2                                                              
                                                                                
         GOTOR (#IOEXEC,AIOEXEC),'IOSQ+IODIR+IO2'                               
         JNE   SCHINIX                                                          
                                                                                
