         ICM   RF,3,CUXPNUM        Check whether Brandocean rewrite             
         CHI   RF,XPRODIKQ          app is connected                            
         J     SETCCC              If not don't include                         
                                                                                
EDTDFLT  LM    R2,R4,LP_AINP                                                    
         MVI   0(R4),NOQ                                                        
         CLC   DOMDEF,0(R2)                                                     
         JNE   EDTDFLT2                                                         
         MVI   0(R4),YESQ                                                       
