         CLC   CONCM,SPACES                                                     
         JE    OVTIM30                                                          
         OC    CONCM,CONCM         ANY NOTIFICATION NEEDED?                     
         JZ    OVTIM30                                                          
         ZAP   DUB1,CONCM                                                       
         JZ    OVTIM30                                                          
         CVB   RF,DUB1                                                          
         STCM  RF,3,NTFY#                                                       
         MR    RE,R1                                                            
