OVTIM30  CLC   CONCL,SPACES                                                     
         JE    OVTIM35                                                          
*&&US*&& OC    CONCL,CONCL         ANY NOTIFICATION NEEDED?                     
*&&US*&& JE    OVTIM35                                                          
