         SPACE 1                                                                
SETLAV   NTR1  LABEL=NO                                                         
         J     *+12                                                             
         DC    C'*SETLAV*'                                                      
*                                                                               
         LR    R2,R1               Company extra element                        
N        USING CPXELD,R2                                                        
         LAY   R3,CPXTAB                                                        
         USING CPXTABD,R3                                                       
         LHI   RF,CPXTABN                                                       
SETLAV04 LLC   R1,CPXTVAL                                                       
         LA    R4,LL_DACS(R1)                                                   
