         USING OFFALD,R1                                                        
         L     R1,AOFFAREA                                                      
         MVC   OFFAOFFC,OFFKOFF    move in offices                              
         MVI   OFFAACT,OFFAVAL                                                  
         GOTO1 VOFFAL                                                           
         JNE   EXITN                                                            
