*** Key filter routine for 2D ACTRECD ***                                       
A2DKF    NTR1                                                                   
         USING ACTRECD,R2                                                       
         LA    R2,IOKEY                                                         
         CLC   ACTKACT,SPACES                                                   
         JE    EXITN                                                            
         LA    RE,ACTKACT+1                                                     
