         JNE   EXITN                                                            
                                                                                
         CLI   LP_ACCS,0           skip if no limit access                      
         JE    EXITY                                                            
         USING OFFALD,R1                                                        
         L     R1,AOFFAREA                                                      
         MVC   OFFAOFFC,ACTKACT    move in offices                              
         MVI   OFFAACT,OFFAVAL                                                  
         GOTO1 VOFFAL                                                           
         JNE   EXITN                                                            
         J     EXITY                                                            
