*** Record filter routine for Client record ***                                 
CLIRF    NTR1                                                                   
         L     R1,AIO4                                                          
         USING ACTRECD,R1                                                       
         LA    R2,ACTRFST                                                       
         LR    R4,R2                                                            
         USING PPRELD,R2                                                        
CLIRF02  CLI   PPREL,0                                                          
         JE    EXITY                                                            
         CLI   PPREL,PPRELQ                                                     
         JE    CLIRF04                                                          
         LLC   R0,PPRLN                                                         
         AR    R2,R0                                                            
         J     CLIRF02                                                          
CLIRF04  CLC   PPRGAOFF,SPACES                                                  
         JNH   EXITY                                                            
         USING LW_D,R3                                                          
         XR    R3,R3               Point to list in WMP                         
         ICM   R3,7,DAOFF                                                       
         JZ    CLIRF12                                                          
         XR    R0,R0                                                            
         ICM   R0,3,LW_NUMN        Number of entries                            
         JZ    EXITY                                                            
