CLIRF06  CLC   PPRGAOFF,0(R3)                                                   
         JE    CLIRF12                                                          
         AHI   R3,L'PPRGAOFF                                                    
         JCT   R0,CLIRF06                                                       
         J     EXITN                                                            
                                                                                
