***********************************************************************         
* Get rate for VAT code                                               *         
* NTRY: R1 = 0 VAT/GST CODE, Province code (PST code)                 *         
***********************************************************************         
         SPACE 1                                                                
         USING VTCD,R2                                                          
RATCOD   NTR1  LABEL=*                                                          
         J     *+12                                                             
         DC    C'*RATCOD*'                                                      
*                                                                               
         STC   R1,BYTE1                                                         
         MVC   BYTE2,EL_PSTCD      Set to PST code                              
