         USING CASRECD,R2                                                       
         LA    R2,IOKEY                                                         
         XC    CASKEY,CASKEY                                                    
         MVI   CASKTYP,CASKTYPQ                                                 
         MVI   CASKSUB,CASKSUBQ                                                 
         MVC   CASKCPY,CUXCPY                                                   
         MVC   CASKEMOA,DCEND                                                   
